channel.title: Highest skills you achieved with autoing
channel.description:
for those of u who have autoed, whats the highest skills youve obtained?
I ve never autoed in rs2 due to randoms and jagex's auto detection, but b4 rsc was made p2p only i ran a bot for several hours and got a noob acc to lvl 64 or so firemaking.
however, ive seen things more impressive, lol, such as a rsc account with over 70m fishing exp, or several lvl 99 stats (including smithing and crafting, which are hell on rsc).
I know theres lvl 99 wcers and fishers autoed on rs2.
whats the farthest you've gone?
obviously dont post your usernames lol as jagex probably reads this forum
